program NewbienewtysHighAlcher;
{.include SRL/SRL.scar}
{.include SRL/SRL/skill/magic.scar}
Const
TotalNeeded = 128;
GoldPerItem = 1234; //Gold Per Item
item = ‘Item Alching Here’; //Item Name(For Report)
InvNumber = 20; //Amount In Inventory You want Alched

var
TotalDone : Integer;

Procedure ChangeReport;
begin
cleardebug;
TotalDone:= TotalDone + 1;
writeln(‘High Alched’ + inttostr(TotalDone) + ‘’ + (Item));
Writeln(‘Made’ + inttostr(totalDone*GoldPerItem) + ’ times left’);
end;

Procedure HighAlch;
begin
repeat
setupsrl;
Gametab(7);
fixmage(true);
castspell(31)
MouseItem(InvNumber, true)
Wait(Random(23)+2400);
ChangeReport;
Until(TotalDone = TotalNeeded);
logout;
end;
begin
end.
